Text: Decent set, averaging 600kb per pic. She has a touch of extra weight on her than is popular thesedays, it's nice too see for a change, more like a regular girl I suppose. I'm not a big fan of the apprehensive/scared look on her face that seems to be the sets theme though. Nothing nasty but.. Maybe it's me picking up on something that was unintended, who knows.. Anyway, good of you to Reupload a request for someone 5-click.
